    <item>
      <title>巴里克黄金公司首席执行官谈第四季度业绩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-12/barrick-gold-ceo-on-4q-results-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴里克黄金公司今天公布了第四季度业绩。收入同比增长近 20%，但该公司预计今年黄金产量将放缓。巴里克黄金公司首席执行官马克·布里斯托 (Mark Bristow) 参加了彭博公开收益 (Bloomberg Open Interest) 节目，谈论了公司的业绩以及黄金的前景。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-12/barrick-gold-ceo-on-4q-results-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 15:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈塞特称特朗普将解决通胀问题并降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-12/trump-will-fix-inflation-bring-rates-down-hassett-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫国家经济委员会主任凯文·哈塞特表示，无论有没有美联储，唐纳德·特朗普总统都会解决通胀问题。他说，随着财政责任的增加，利率和通胀将会下降。他在“彭博未平仓合约”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-12/trump-will-fix-inflation-bring-rates-down-hassett-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 15:29:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约证券交易所计划在德克萨斯州开设交易所，因金融公司纷纷涌入该州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/nyse-opens-new-exchange-in-texas-in-push-to-capture-ipo-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约证券交易所计划在德克萨斯州开设一家股票交易所，这是最新一家寻求在税收较低、监管较宽松的州分得金融服务业份额的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/nyse-opens-new-exchange-in-texas-in-push-to-capture-ipo-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 14:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西石油公司首席执行官称特朗普上任后可应对油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/petrobras-can-cope-with-cheaper-oil-under-trump-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西石油公司首席执行官玛格达·尚布里亚德 (Magda Chambriard) 表示，这家巴西石油巨头可以承受唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导下的全球油价小幅下滑，部分原因是依靠其在中国和印度的客户。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/petrobras-can-cope-with-cheaper-oil-under-trump-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 14:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德的信贷部门现在是其最大的资产来源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/brookfield-s-credit-arm-is-now-its-largest-source-of-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理公司第四季度筹集了 290 亿美元，其中大部分来自其信贷业务，这已成为其最大的增长动力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/brookfield-s-credit-arm-is-now-its-largest-source-of-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 11:50:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税计划导致日元跌至一周最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/yen-underperforms-major-currencies-on-trump-tariff-uncertainties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于人们对日本可能被纳入唐纳德·特朗普关税计划的担忧加剧，加上美元走强，日元有望创下一个多月以来最长的连续下跌势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-12/yen-underperforms-major-currencies-on-trump-tariff-uncertainties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Feb 2025 03:29:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
